; Card maize-122: the float operands of a same-format op must be the same width.
; Mixing binary32 (H0) and binary64 (W0) is illegal; mazm must reject it at
; assemble time (the VM also traps it deterministically at run time). Here FADD
; names a binary32 source and a binary64 destination.

$0000`0000:
    CP $3FC00000 R0.H0
    FADD R0.H0 R1.W0
    HALT
